INSERT INTO articles_articles VALUES(1,'西北的陕西，旅游好去处，自然风光太吸引人','articles/timg_3.jpeg','2019-05-07 17:57:00',5,0,12,1,'<p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 24px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-align: justify; font-family: arial; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><span class="bjh-p">我相信很多人都会把陕西省作为自己旅行目的地之一，我相信，很多人都知道，这里的每一个地方，每一座城市，都很好玩。他们有的是被历史打磨的非常的好，有的是自然风光太吸引人了。今天我们一起来看看，陕西的哪一些城市，可以走走看看瞧一瞧，让你的旅行变得非常有意义。</span></p><p><img class="large" data-loadfunc="0" src="https://ss1.baidu.com/6ONXsjip0QIZ8tyhnq/it/u=4226496769,2451710786&fm=173&app=25&f=JPEG?w=640&h=480&s=6A3000C547AEBEEA541514150300C0C2" data-loaded="0" style="border: 0px; width: 537px; display: block;"/> </p><p style="margin-top: 26px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 24px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-align: justify; font-family: arial; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><span class="bjh-p">第一个，就要说说西安了。在西安的话，好玩的东西太多了，比如说最著名的就是秦始皇兵马俑。我相信不管是来自国内的游客还是国外的游客，都知道这个景点。现在出土的就有1000多个用陶做的陶俑士兵。</span></p><p style="margin-top: 22px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 24px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-align: justify; font-family: arial; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><span class="bjh-p">不光士兵的数量多，而且每一个的造型都不一样，表情都不一样，这就很神奇了。所以我们都说它是世界上的第八大奇迹。</span></p><p><img class="large" data-loadfunc="0" src="https://ss1.baidu.com/6ONXsjip0QIZ8tyhnq/it/u=273132601,282154283&fm=173&app=25&f=JPEG?w=640&h=427&s=7CAABF57F491F3C65880C4450300F0E7" data-loaded="0" style="border: 0px; width: 537px; display: block;"/> </p><p style="margin-top: 26px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 24px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-align: justify; font-family: arial; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><span class="bjh-p">西安是一座很老的城市，除了有历史这么这么悠久的兵马俑，还有比如说西安的城墙也可以去看一看，虽然历史很久了，但是这里的古代城墙还是保存得十分的好。<span class="bjh-br"></span></span></p><p><img class="large" data-loadfunc="0" src="https://ss1.baidu.com/6ONXsjip0QIZ8tyhnq/it/u=3075120031,496840997&fm=173&app=25&f=JPEG?w=640&h=427&s=7F5004C685FF122D0AAB37360300C058" data-loaded="0" style="border: 0px; width: 537px; display: block;"/> </p><p style="margin-top: 26px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 24px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-align: justify; font-family: arial; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><span class="bjh-p">还有就是大同芙蓉园了。我相信唐朝那样繁华的盛世，每个人都想去看一看，究竟是怎么样的。这里是所有的建筑都是唐朝的式样，有时候还会上演大型的舞台剧，所以一定要来这里瞧一瞧。<span class="bjh-br"></span></span></p><p style="margin-top: 22px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 24px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-align: justify; font-family: arial; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><span class="bjh-p">除了西安之外，延安也是一定要去的地方。西安可能更多的是中国古代的一些历史影响，而在延安的话，那就是红色旅游的圣地了。在这里，你能看到各式各样的旧的革命旧址。在这些窑洞里面，你可以充分感受那个时候我们的革命先烈们在这里付出的努力。</span></p><p><img class="large" data-loadfunc="0" src="https://ss0.baidu.com/6ONWsjip0QIZ8tyhnq/it/u=326827044,2601205808&fm=173&app=25&f=JPEG?w=640&h=417&s=B9D86D865C4B2AC64A89393C03005050" data-loaded="0" style="border: 0px; width: 537px; display: block;"/> </p><p style="margin-top: 26px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 24px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-align: justify; font-family: arial; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><span class="bjh-p">当然，延安不仅有历史，还有非常美妙的自然风光。比如说很有名的壶口瀑布就在这里压壶口瀑布算是黄河上一个比较有名的景点。瀑布的水流非常非常的急，而且落差非常的大，所以在这里你能看到波涛汹涌澎湃。来这里你也可以看一看历史非常久远，可以追溯到唐代的宝塔山。<span class="bjh-br"></span></span></p><p style="margin-top: 22px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 24px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-align: justify; font-family: arial; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><span class="bjh-p">其实西安除了这两座城市之外，别的城市历史也非常的悠久。比如说我们再来说一座你也可以去玩一玩的城市，那就是咸阳。咸阳的话其实你在我们古代的历史上都会听到这个名字，甚至比西安还要有名，那是因为这是对我国古代历史非常重要的一座城市。</span></p><p><img class="large" data-loadfunc="0" src="https://ss0.baidu.com/6ONWsjip0QIZ8tyhnq/it/u=3325986912,3125291053&fm=173&app=25&f=JPEG?w=640&h=360&s=DF5A23D38ED138CC6A016C240300E0E2" data-loaded="0" style="border: 0px; width: 537px; display: block;"/> </p><p style="margin-top: 26px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 24px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-align: justify; font-family: arial; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><span class="bjh-p">在这里呀，你可以去乾陵，茂陵，汉阳陵博物馆，懿德太子墓，永泰公主墓等等地方，充分感受一下我们古代的历史。<span class="bjh-br"></span></span></p><p style="margin-top: 22px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 24px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-align: justify; font-family: arial; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><span class="bjh-p">当然了，还有一个最重要的景点就是在渭南的华山。这也是中国非常有名的一座名山了，他被称作是西岳。华山真的是很险峻，山形地貌也非常的奇特，所以如果你是登山爱好者的话，来陕西省一定要去华山，做一回勇士好汉。</span></p><p><img class="large" data-loadfunc="0" src="https://ss2.baidu.com/6ONYsjip0QIZ8tyhnq/it/u=1537889357,1326463430&fm=173&app=25&f=JPEG?w=640&h=427&s=B3BF5184D29939CE6E2CD5C40300E0B9" data-loaded="0" style="border: 0px; width: 537px; display: block;"/> </p><p style="margin-top: 26px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 24px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-align: justify; font-family: arial; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><span class="bjh-p">总得来说，我觉得陕西省的这几座城市都是非常值得一去的，他们既有历史人文，风光，因为我们美丽的自然风景，而且相得益彰，很好地满足了有不同旅游喜好的人们。</span></p><p><br/> </p>',1,'背上背包你可远行：去雪域西藏朝圣，到川蜀美食，游丽江观玉龙雪山.......');
INSERT INTO articles_articles VALUES(2,'层次越高的人，越能发现生活中的美学','articles/timg_1.jpeg','2019-05-07 18:17:00',0,0,0,1,'<p style="margin-top: 22px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 24px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-align: justify; font-family: arial; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><span class="bjh-p">01</span></p><p style="margin-top: 22px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 24px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-align: justify; font-family: arial; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><span class="bjh-p"><span class="bjh-br"></span></span></p><p style="margin-top: 22px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 24px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-align: justify; font-family: arial; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><span class="bjh-p">日复一日地生活，总是如此匆忙。</span></p><p style="margin-top: 22px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 24px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-align: justify; font-family: arial; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><span class="bjh-p"><span class="bjh-br"></span></span></p><p style="margin-top: 22px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 24px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-align: justify; font-family: arial; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><span class="bjh-blockquote" style="display: block; position: relative; font-size: 18px; color: rgb(153, 153, 153); padding-left: 30px; min-height: 24px;"><span class="bjh-p">你有多久没有好好地观赏夜空中的月亮了？</span><span class="bjh-p">你有多久没有静下心来看一本书，品一杯茶了？</span><span class="bjh-p">你有多久没有犒劳自己一顿摆盘精致的晚餐了？</span></span></p><p style="margin-top: 22px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 24px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-align: justify; font-family: arial; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><span class="bjh-p"><span class="bjh-br"></span></span></p><p style="margin-top: 22px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 24px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-align: justify; font-family: arial; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><span class="bjh-p">你是时候该停下来，感受、享受周围的一切了。</span></p><p style="margin-top: 22px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 24px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-align: justify; font-family: arial; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><span class="bjh-p"><span class="bjh-br"></span></span></p><p style="margin-top: 22px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 24px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-align: justify; font-family: arial; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><span class="bjh-p">美学大师蒋勋在《品味四讲》中，也传达了这样的理念：</span></p><p style="margin-top: 22px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 24px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-align: justify; font-family: arial; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><span class="bjh-p"><span class="bjh-br"></span></span></p><p style="margin-top: 22px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 24px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-align: justify; font-family: arial; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><span class="bjh-blockquote" style="display: block; position: relative; font-size: 18px; color: rgb(153, 153, 153); padding-left: 30px; min-height: 24px;"><span class="bjh-p">天地有大美而不言，美无处不在，我们要放缓节奏，感受生活中的点滴之美。</span></span></p><p style="margin-top: 22px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 24px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-align: justify; font-family: arial; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><span class="bjh-p"><span class="bjh-br"></span></span></p><p><img class="large" data-loadfunc="0" src="http://t12.baidu.com/it/u=2285003678,2386473074&fm=173&app=25&f=JPEG?w=640&h=427&s=4F00D50C3079A3843FA439C6030040AD" data-loaded="0" style="border: 0px; width: 537px; display: block;"/></p><p style="margin-top: 26px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 24px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-align: justify; font-family: arial; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><span class="bjh-p"><span class="bjh-br"></span></span></p><p style="margin-top: 22px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 24px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-align: justify; font-family: arial; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><span class="bjh-p">02<span class="bjh-br"></span></span></p><p style="margin-top: 22px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 24px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-align: justify; font-family: arial; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><span class="bjh-p"><span class="bjh-br"></span></span></p><p style="margin-top: 22px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 24px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-align: justify; font-family: arial; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><span class="bjh-p"><span class="bjh-strong" style="font-size: 18px; font-weight: 700;">认识美的重要开始：吃</span></span></p><p style="margin-top: 22px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 24px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-align: justify; font-family: arial; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><span class="bjh-p"><span class="bjh-br"></span></span></p><p style="margin-top: 22px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 24px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-align: justify; font-family: arial; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><span class="bjh-p">我们不难发现，在与朋友聊起生命中美好回忆时，其中会有很多跟吃东西有关。大家会谈起在哪里吃了生命，哪里又吃了什么。</span></p><p style="margin-top: 22px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 24px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-align: justify; font-family: arial; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><span class="bjh-p"><span class="bjh-br"></span></span></p><p style="margin-top: 22px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 24px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-align: justify; font-family: arial; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><span class="bjh-p">吃，是认识美的一个重要开始，如果吃的粗糙、乱七八糟，其他的美大概也就很难讲究了。</span></p><p style="margin-top: 22px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 24px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-align: justify; font-family: arial; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><span class="bjh-p"><span class="bjh-br"></span></span></p><p style="margin-top: 22px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 24px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-align: justify; font-family: arial; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><span class="bjh-p">在烹饪意大利海鲜汤时，你是否会在揉碎的月桂叶中，联想到太阳神阿波罗和变为月桂树的达芙妮之间的故事？</span></p><p style="margin-top: 22px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 24px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-align: justify; font-family: arial; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><span class="bjh-p"><span class="bjh-br"></span></span></p><p style="margin-top: 22px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 24px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-align: justify; font-family: arial; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><span class="bjh-p">你是否会在白酒的香气中想起温暖的阳光，肥沃的土壤和滋润的雨水？</span></p><p style="margin-top: 22px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 24px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-align: justify; font-family: arial; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><span class="bjh-p"><span class="bjh-br"></span></span></p><p style="margin-top: 22px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 24px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-align: justify; font-family: arial; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><span class="bjh-p">食物都是富有特殊的意义的，我们可以对食物产生许多情感上的体验：</span></p><p style="margin-top: 22px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 24px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-align: justify; font-family: arial; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><span class="bjh-p"><span class="bjh-br"></span></span></p><p style="margin-top: 22px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 24px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-align: justify; font-family: arial; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><span class="bjh-blockquote" style="display: block; position: relative; font-size: 18px; color: rgb(153, 153, 153); padding-left: 30px; min-height: 24px;"><span class="bjh-p">你会在脑海里浮现一些好像始终忘不掉的食物和料理，它们不只是口感上的回忆，不只是美食当期那种口腔里的快乐，甚至会变成很特别的视觉记忆、嗅觉记忆，甚至会让你在心灵上有一些特别的感动。</span></span></p><p style="margin-top: 22px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 24px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-align: justify; font-family: arial; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><span class="bjh-p"><span class="bjh-br"></span></span></p><p style="margin-top: 22px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 24px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-align: justify; font-family: arial; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><span class="bjh-p">很多人都说世界上最好吃的饭是妈妈做的饭，这大概也是其中所包含的爱与关怀，使得食物变得更加与众不同，更加美味难忘吧。这种时候，食物就远远不只是食物了。</span></p><p style="margin-top: 22px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 24px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-align: justify; font-family: arial; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><span class="bjh-p"><span class="bjh-br"></span></span></p><p style="margin-top: 22px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 24px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-align: justify; font-family: arial; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><span class="bjh-p">因此，希望大家能对食物用心、讲究，在自己的生活里，好好为自己完成生命的菜肴。</span></p><p style="margin-top: 22px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 24px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-align: justify; font-family: arial; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><span class="bjh-p"><span class="bjh-br"></span></span></p><p><img class="large" data-loadfunc="0" src="http://t11.baidu.com/it/u=4234608478,2130121063&fm=173&app=25&f=JPEG?w=640&h=427&s=A680D70554E5850DF30575F00300C0B1" data-loaded="0" style="border: 0px; width: 537px; display: block;"/></p><p style="margin-top: 26px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 24px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-align: justify; font-family: arial; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><span class="bjh-p"><span class="bjh-br"></span></span></p><p style="margin-top: 22px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 24px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-align: justify; font-family: arial; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><span class="bjh-p">03<span class="bjh-br"></span></span></p><p style="margin-top: 22px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 24px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-align: justify; font-family: arial; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><span class="bjh-p"><span class="bjh-br"></span></span></p><p style="margin-top: 22px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 24px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-align: justify; font-family: arial; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><span class="bjh-p"><span class="bjh-strong" style="font-size: 18px; font-weight: 700;">衣服之美</span></span></p><p style="margin-top: 22px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 24px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-align: justify; font-family: arial; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><span class="bjh-p"><span class="bjh-br"></span></span></p><p style="margin-top: 22px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 24px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-align: justify; font-family: arial; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><span class="bjh-p">与我们生活息息相关的美，除了食物之外，就是衣服了。衣服大概是生活之美最直接的体现，无论是服装、鞋子，都是一个人身体的记忆。</span></p><p style="margin-top: 22px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 24px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-align: justify; font-family: arial; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><span class="bjh-p"><span class="bjh-br"></span></span></p><p style="margin-top: 22px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 24px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-align: justify; font-family: arial; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><span class="bjh-p">一件你喜爱的衣服，真的就像一位好朋友，甚至是一个爱人。</span></p><p style="margin-top: 22px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 24px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-align: justify; font-family: arial; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><span class="bjh-p"><span class="bjh-br"></span></span></p><p style="margin-top: 22px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 24px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-align: justify; font-family: arial; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><span class="bjh-p">我很喜爱的纯棉衬衫，衬衫里有长久穿着的记忆，于是就会对它们多花一些心血。舍不得用洗衣机去洗，而是用手揉搓干净，我觉得这也是一种快乐。</span></p><p style="margin-top: 22px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 24px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-align: justify; font-family: arial; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><span class="bjh-p"><span class="bjh-br"></span></span></p><p style="margin-top: 22px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 24px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-align: justify; font-family: arial; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><span class="bjh-p">你是否也有几件特别珍惜的衣服，即使穿了很久也舍不得扔掉的呢？</span></p><p style="margin-top: 22px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 24px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-align: justify; font-family: arial; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><span class="bjh-p"><span class="bjh-br"></span></span></p><p style="margin-top: 22px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 24px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-align: justify; font-family: arial; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><span class="bjh-p">许多人都喜爱名牌，盲目追求昂贵价格的衣物，但却不明白自己为什么会喜欢这件衣服。</span></p><p style="margin-top: 22px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 24px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-align: justify; font-family: arial; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><span class="bjh-p"><span class="bjh-br"></span></span></p><p style="margin-top: 22px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 24px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-align: justify; font-family: arial; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><span class="bjh-p">美不是价格，而是物质被经过思考后产生的不同情感，这可能是亲情，也可能是爱情与友谊。当这些情谊被编织进一件衣服里时，已经无法用价格衡量了。</span></p><p style="margin-top: 22px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 24px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-align: justify; font-family: arial; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><span class="bjh-p"><span class="bjh-br"></span></span></p><p style="margin-top: 22px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 24px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-align: justify; font-family: arial; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><span class="bjh-p">就像《品味四讲》中的一个例子：</span></p><p style="margin-top: 22px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 24px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-align: justify; font-family: arial; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><span class="bjh-p"><span class="bjh-br"></span></span></p><p style="margin-top: 22px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 24px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-align: justify; font-family: arial; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><span class="bjh-blockquote" style="display: block; position: relative; font-size: 18px; color: rgb(153, 153, 153); padding-left: 30px; min-height: 24px;"><span class="bjh-p">许多母亲健在的人，大概不会觉得她为你织了一件毛衣，你穿在身上就会有多么伟大、永恒的力量。</span><span class="bjh-p"><span class="bjh-br"></span></span><span class="bjh-p">但如果你发现一位朋友冬天老爱穿同一件陈旧的毛衣时，你可能会觉得奇怪，还会跟他建议买一件毛衣。</span><span class="bjh-p"><span class="bjh-br"></span></span><span class="bjh-p">然而他却告诉你，“这件毛衣是我过世的母亲织给我的。”</span></span></p><p style="margin-top: 22px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 24px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-align: justify; font-family: arial; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><span class="bjh-p"><span class="bjh-br"></span></span></p><p style="margin-top: 22px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 24px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-align: justify; font-family: arial; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><span class="bjh-p">这个时候你肯定会悚然一惊，你就知道，他到任何地方去买再昂贵的衣服，都比不上这件毛衣所包含的温暖了。</span></p><p style="margin-top: 22px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 24px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-align: justify; font-family: arial; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><span class="bjh-p"><span class="bjh-br"></span></span></p><p style="margin-top: 22px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 24px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-align: justify; font-family: arial; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><span class="bjh-p">衣物的美，不只在于款式，更不在与价格，最美的衣物里，必然拥有最动人的情谊。</span></p><p style="margin-top: 22px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 24px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-align: justify; font-family: arial; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><span class="bjh-p"><span class="bjh-br"></span></span></p><p><img class="large" data-loadfunc="0" src="http://t12.baidu.com/it/u=2161485485,281420083&fm=173&app=25&f=JPEG?w=640&h=427&s=B9992BDBD403D8EC04B960300300C042" data-loaded="0" style="border: 0px; width: 537px; display: block;"/></p><p style="margin-top: 26px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 24px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-align: justify; font-family: arial; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><span class="bjh-p"><span class="bjh-br"></span></span></p><p style="margin-top: 22px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 24px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-align: justify; font-family: arial; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><span class="bjh-p">04</span></p><p style="margin-top: 22px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 24px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-align: justify; font-family: arial; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><span class="bjh-p"><span class="bjh-br"></span></span></p><p style="margin-top: 22px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 24px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-align: justify; font-family: arial; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><span class="bjh-p">蒋勋说：缓慢，恐怕是建立生命美学品质的第一步。无论衣食住行，希望我们的生活都能有慢下来的可能。</span></p><p style="margin-top: 22px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 24px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-align: justify; font-family: arial; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><span class="bjh-p"><span class="bjh-br"></span></span></p><p style="margin-top: 22px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 24px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-align: justify; font-family: arial; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><span class="bjh-p">然而肯定会有人反问，每天忙着工作、忙着所有繁杂的事务，怎么可能缓慢？</span></p><p style="margin-top: 22px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 24px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-align: justify; font-family: arial; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><span class="bjh-p"><span class="bjh-br"></span></span></p><p style="margin-top: 22px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 24px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-align: justify; font-family: arial; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><span class="bjh-p">对此，蒋勋认为，缓慢本身，要架构在“心情”上。忙，就是心亡，所以如何让自己心境悠闲就变得十分重要。</span></p><p style="margin-top: 22px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 24px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-align: justify; font-family: arial; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><span class="bjh-p"><span class="bjh-br"></span></span></p><p style="margin-top: 22px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 24px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-align: justify; font-family: arial; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><span class="bjh-p">人生，应是可以随时停下来缓慢行走的一条路，而不是一条快速的高速公路。</span></p><p style="margin-top: 22px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 24px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-align: justify; font-family: arial; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><span class="bjh-p"><span class="bjh-br"></span></span></p><p style="margin-top: 22px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 24px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-align: justify; font-family: arial; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><span class="bjh-p">你准备好慢下来，发现生活中的美了吗？</span></p><p><br/></p>',5,'你有多久没有好好地观赏夜空中的月亮了？你有多久没有静下心来看一本书，品一杯茶了？');
